Git-commit: 7c5dd23e57c14cf7177b8a5e0fd08916e0c60005

[ Upstream commit 7c5dd23e57c14cf7177b8a5e0fd08916e0c60005 ]

Remove devm_* allocation and fix wq->conf_dev 'struct device' lifetime.
